summary: This is an AT&T telephone call detail record for a specific landline number (561-308-0282), covering calls from 2002 to 2006, produced in 2019 for a law enforcement matter. It logs incoming and outgoing calls, showing communication patterns and connections to numerous other phone numbers during this period.
